        <h1>Ethical Considerations for Developers</h1>
        <p>Developers must ensure that their software respects privacy, promotes transparency, and does not discriminate against users.</p>
        <p>For example, data scientists should follow guidelines like the ACM Code of Ethics, ensuring fair and unbiased treatment of data.</p>

        <p><strong>Reference:</strong> ACM Code of Ethics, <a href="https://www.acm.org/code-of-ethics" target="_blank">https://www.acm.org/code-of-ethics</a></p>
